	(19689,107,'wpcf-biography','I am Viktoria Hristova from Varna, Bulgaria. In school I have received numerous certificates of acknowledgment for my artistic abilities, participated in a great amount of art exhibitions and have won several awards.\r\n\r\nI am inspired by my travels and the unique qualities of each place I visit. I enjoy experimenting with different artistic materials, and combining them in my art pieces. This has led to my passion for making collages. I enjoy the non-traditional process, which results in an abstract piece of art.'),
