	(20979,88,'wpcf-biography','Israeli by origin and demeanor, obsessed with TV and practicality. \r\nIn the past: Animals - volunteer work; IDF military service - boot camp commander; undergraduate degree - industrial design; internships in NY - IDEO, Kikkerland, HUGE. \r\nCurrently: Master of Fine Arts - Design and Technology program at Parsons. \r\nIn the future: UX Designer somewhere fun, making products that people will be happy to use.'),
