	(20987,78,'wpcf-biography','I am Mauricio, a Colombian designer who worked as an industrial designer prior to joining the MFA Design and Technology program. Before Parsons, I did product development, focusing on furniture and lighting. Then I worked in digital fabrication, which was my first exposure to technology. During my time here at Parsons, I built upon my existing skill set, focusing on experiential projects that connect hardware and software to create unique experiences.'),
