	(21075,79,'wpcf-biography','Maxine is an animal lover and loves to cook.\r\nShe was born in South Korea, immigrated to Canada when she was 17, then moved to New York to achieve what she loves.  \r\nHer visceral approach to interaction design has lead her to focus on tactile interfaces at the intersection of materiality and computation. She is an interactive/creative technologist who is fascinated by aesthetic qualities of human experience blended with technology.'),
