	(21078,79,'wpcf-twitter','maxinejykim'),
	(21079,83,'wpcf-biography','Minsung loves making things to explore her creativity and express her design thought. Before studying at Parsons MFA Design and Technology, she was an artist in South Korea. In Korea, she struggled with her calling and how to use art in a more meaningful way. She believes that combining art and technology together would make the communication between people more efficient, and that technology has brought various innovative possibilities to the traditional understanding of art. She uses such methods to make people think about things they would normally overlook.'),
