	(24954,533,'wpcf-long-description','The Diaspora is a web based project that explores how Asian internationals in New York feel about their original culture after dislocation. This project includes stories and perspectives of 20 internationals from China, Korea, India, Taiwan and Thailand. It shares their personal views on the cultural values they hold on to the most, and those cultural values they want to leave behind.\r\nThe Diaspora hopes to spread awareness of how we are changed after being dislocated and how globalization has affected us.'),
