	(26725,114,'wpcf-biography','My name is Z. I was born in 1990.  Machines fuel my life. My phone, my\r\nprinter and my triple heart bypass are all machines. Even a deeper\r\npart of me is a machine, the cold, logical, productive part. I despise\r\nthat part, although I love it as well. So what I do is make art. I’m\r\nvery good at making animatronics and robotic sculptures. Video art is\r\nmy other big interest.  I’m also very skilled at physical computing,\r\nProcessing, openFrameworks, web and graphic design.'),
