	(26766,503,'wpcf-long-description','Transcendence is built to explore the parallels between modern physics and Eastern mysticism such as Buddhism.   It helps people reach the understanding of what is believed to be true happiness, real purpose of life, the enlightenment.  Transcendence ties together notions of spatial controls and body gesture.  It is naturally at the intersection of art and technology.  Projection of real 3 dimensional spaces where a user can interact directly with the space without timing or instruction will be set and allows user to create their personal experiences.'),
